{{future album}}

'''''Time on Earth''''' is the fifth studio album by the pop-rock band [[Crowded House]]. It is due to be released in 2007. ''Time on Earth'' marks the reunion of the band eleven years after they disbanded and features new drummer [[Matt Sherrod]] in place of the original drummer, the late [[Paul Hester]], who took his own life in 2005.


==Personnel==

*[[Neil Finn]]: vocals, acoustic and electric guitars
*[[Nick Seymour]]: bass, backing vocals
*[[Mark Hart]]: keyboards, electric guitar, backing vocals
*[[Matt Sherrod]]: drums

